Epic Fights<br>
<br>
1. Eejag in Lavastorm - 55, hits 160ish, summons, is hit by fire spells which is odd because he is ROOTED in the middle of the lava lake outside Sol B. Visibility is supposed to be very bad for the fight. Folks recommend having casters on the bottom of the lake instead of on the banks out of the lava. Lava damage gets down to 10-12 per tick with good resists.<br>
<br>
2. Gwan in Plane of Sky, Noble Dojorns Island - 57, hits 160ish, enrages, summons, almost magic immune (lures from melee range can land) procs a resistable KNOCKBACK which can knock folks off the island so the plan is to pull him into a windmill for the fight. He's triggered, the turnin NPC is a 2 hour spawn.<br>
<br>
3. Trunt in Droga - 59, hits 175, 100% magic immune, procs a 200dd, runs<br>
<br>
4. Final Fight, LoIO<br>
    - Deep and Vorash, 57-59, both hit 170ish, both proc 500dd.  Trigger them, pull from platform to shore and kill.<br>
    - Killing Vorash spawns Xenovorash back out on the platform.  Xeno is 65, hits 250, procs a 500dd + stun, pretty MR<br>
<br>
